article.linkText: Western Carolina secures 78-63 win against UNC Asheville
article.story: CULLOWHEE, N.C. -- — Vonterius Woolbright scored 23 points as Western Carolina beat UNC Asheville 78-63 on Saturday night. Woolbright had 12 rebounds and seven assists for the Catamounts (7-2). Bernard Pelote scored 13 points, going 6 of 8. Tre Jackson had 12 points, going 4 for 6 from 3-point range. Fletcher Abee led the way for the Bulldogs (5-5). Drew Pember added 18 points, six rebounds and five assists for UNC Asheville. In addition, Trent Stephney finished with seven points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
